# Deployment Architecture
- Frontend: Vercel (React.js/Vite)
- Backend: Render (Node.js/Express)
- Database: Supabase (Postgres)
    - Development: Local Docker instance via Supabase CLI
    - Production: Hosted Supabase Cloud (Postgres)

# Networking Logic
- Local Dev: Backend talks to Supabase via 'host.docker.internal:54322'
- Production: Backend talks to Supabase via Connection String (Cloud URL)
- CORS: Backend on Render must allow requests from the Vercel frontend URL.

# Database Management
- Use Supabase CLI for all migrations.
- NEVER suggest 'Developing in Production'. 
- All schema changes must be generated as migrations in the /supabase/migrations folder.